'''Huanghe Hydropower''''s '''Golmud Solar park''' is a 200 [[megawatt]] (MW) [[photovoltaic power station]] located in [[Golmud]], [[Qinghai Province]], [[China]].<ref name=cluster>{{cite web|title=Golmud Desert Solar Cluster - satellite view|url=http://www.wiki-solar.org/map/sites/index.html?Golmud_Desert_Cluster?a?12?36.37?95.18|publisher=Wiki-Solar|accessdate=13 August 2013}}</ref> Construction began in August 2009,<ref>[http://www.thebioenergysite.com/news/4403/largest-solar-power-plant-begins-construction Largest Solar Power Plant Begins Construction]</ref> and it was commissioned on October 29, 2011.<ref>[http://newscontent.cctv.com/news.jsp?fileId=120151 China-PV Power Station] "Restrictions: Not access Chinese mainland"</ref><ref>[http://www.accendo.ro/news/res/74-golmud-solar-park China PV plant largest in the world ] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120405034226/http://www.accendo.ro/news/res/74-golmud-solar-park |date=2012-04-05 }}</ref> 80&nbsp;MW was provided by [[Yingli]].<ref>[http://www.solarnovus.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=3103:yingli-green-energy-to-supply-110-mw-of-pv-modules-to-huanghe-hydropower&catid=37:business-news&Itemid=241 Yingli Green Energy to Supply 110 MW of PV Modules to Huanghe Hydropower]</ref> The project won the 2012 China Quality Power Project Award. Output is expected to be 317&nbsp;[[GWh]] per year.<ref>[http://eng.cpicorp.com.cn/NewsCenter/CorporateNews/201206/t20120607_200313.htm Golmud 200MW PV Station Won China Quality Power Project Award] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725025143/http://eng.cpicorp.com.cn/NewsCenter/CorporateNews/201206/t20120607_200313.htm |date=2012-07-25 }}</ref>
Also in Golmud is the 20&nbsp;MW [[Qinghai Golmud Solar Park]] completed in 2011 by Longyuan Power, as well as others.<ref>[http://www.pvsolarchina.com/chint-solar-successfully-completed-golmud-20mw-photovoltaic-power-station.html Chint Solar successfully completed Golmud 20&nbsp;MW photovoltaic power station]</ref><ref>[http://www.suntrix.cn/home-en/news-events/company-news/golmud.aspx Suntrix Golmud Project Shows Extraordinary Effect in the Qinghai-Tibet Plateau]</ref><ref>[http://www.renewbl.com/2011/11/11/astronergy-completes-20-mw-golmud-solar-project-in-china.html Astronergy completes 20 MW Golmud solar project in China] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120405022737/http://www.renewbl.com/2011/11/11/astronergy-completes-20-mw-golmud-solar-project-in-china.html |date=2012-04-05 }}</ref> There are a total of 570&nbsp;MW of solar parks in Golmud, many of which are located in the Golmud Desert Cluster,<ref name=cluster /> with 500&nbsp;MW more expected in 2012.<ref>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/usa/business/2012-03/02/content_14744509.htm Qinghai leads in photovoltaic power] Updated: 2012-03-02</ref><sup>[''update needed'']</sup>
